result.name: Hung Kee Seafood Restaurant

reviews.text: We tried the 瀨尿蝦 mantis shrimp,crab, oyster, 象拔蚌 geoduck, 虎蝦tiger shrimp.  Overall the seafood is okay.   Some are more fresh than others.  I think the best one are mantis shrimp & geoduck.  The oyster is not fresh and not recommended.
Loved the food here! Friendly staff. Sanitary not great though.
Good Cantonese style seafood. Veggie are a liitle bit plane
The seafood was not bad but it had a bit of fishy smell. The dim sum and other dishes were good and the prices were also reasonable. It is also conveniently located near the taxi and minibus station.

The toilet was suck.. because it has no access for the elderly, it might be difficult for them who doesn't use to traditional toilet. And it's dirty, the price about food even though it's fresh but I think the scale might not right. We order about 1kg squids it's turned only like 5pcs of small size only.. hahaha

reviews.text: 一走隔離就開片😂
覺得好食過隔離米芝蓮介紹果間🙈🙈
食ok,順度去開西貢，都可一試(價錢有啲貴)，但只為食而去，西貢還有好多 美味之選。
中午飯市價錢亦算合理，食物水平可以，晚市就不清楚了。
去咗食茶，D 點心好難食，燒賣又有怪味。相信已變壞。冇下次。
